snippet: Croatian players Borna Coric and Ante Pavic each earned three-set wins over Spanish opponents on Monday to reach the second round of the Chennai Open....
lead_paragraph: Croatian players Borna Coric and Ante Pavic each earned three-set wins over Spanish opponents on Monday to reach the second round of the Chennai Open.

headline.print_headline: Borna Coric, Ante Pavic Advance With 3-Set Wins in Chennai
headline.main: Borna Coric, Ante Pavic Advance With 3-Set Wins in Chennai
